[color=magenta]Something very, very odd[/color]...
=> END

~ monitor_1
Some text is burned onto the weakly flickering monitor.
- Read it
	"The spider-drone fleet's self-replication ability is performing admirably." 
	"Throughout the remainder of this trial period, we will keep an eye on population levels and determine if they rise or fall without influence."
	"Population stability is of utmost importance. Loss of spider-drones will, of course, leave us open to having our hyperspace energy pipelines fed on by local natural entities."
	"An unchecked increase in population could lead to loss of structural integrity. We don't yet know the extent of what the spider-drones will resort to consuming in order to replicate."
	"Log population levels every week."
	=> END
- Don't
=> END

